WEBVTT

00:02.268 --> 00:04.337
<i>PREVIOUSLY ON "THE HAVES</i>
<i>AND THE HAVE NOTS"...</i>

00:04.337 --> 00:06.673
BENNY,
HOW ARE YOU, BABY?

00:06.673 --> 00:07.908
I GOT A HEADACHE.

00:07.908 --> 00:10.243
YEAH, YEAH,
I'LL BET YOU DO.

00:10.243 --> 00:11.778
WHAT'S YOUR LIFE LIKE?

00:11.778 --> 00:14.147
EXCUSE ME?
BEING GAY.

00:14.147 --> 00:16.049
WHO'S THE KID?

00:16.049 --> 00:18.118
MY SON.

00:18.118 --> 00:19.620
WHAT?

00:19.620 --> 00:21.221
IT WAS YOU.

00:21.221 --> 00:22.288
EXCUSE ME?

00:22.288 --> 00:23.289
YOU.

00:23.289 --> 00:25.358
DON'T I KNOW YOU?

00:27.861 --> 00:28.929
KILL HER.

00:28.929 --> 00:31.331
JIM.

00:31.331 --> 00:33.066
[ CHUCKLING ]

00:35.769 --> 00:37.938
I DIDN'T THINK
IT WOULD MATCH, BUT...

00:37.938 --> 00:40.440
OH, THAT'S ALL RIGHT.
OH!

00:40.440 --> 00:42.075
[ Laughing ]
OH, I'M SORRY.

00:42.075 --> 00:44.010
YOU OKAY?

00:44.010 --> 00:46.079
I ALMOST MISSED A STEP,
HUH?

00:46.079 --> 00:47.413
YES, YOU DID.

00:47.413 --> 00:48.448
I'M SORRY.

00:48.448 --> 00:50.083
I'M USUALLY
A MORE GRACEFUL DRUNK.

00:50.083 --> 00:52.853
OKAY.

00:52.853 --> 00:54.120
OKAY, MAGGIE.

00:54.120 --> 00:55.255
YOU FEEL NICE.

00:55.255 --> 00:57.123
LET ME GO NOW.

00:57.123 --> 00:59.392
OH.
I'M SORRY.

00:59.392 --> 01:01.134
I'M ‐‐ NO, I REALLY AM.

01:01.134 --> 01:02.335
NO, IT'S OKAY.

01:02.335 --> 01:04.304
HEY, RELAX.
IT'S FINE.

01:04.304 --> 01:06.773
LOOK AT ME
MAKING A FOOL OF MYSELF.

01:06.773 --> 01:08.108
IT'S FINE.

01:09.208 --> 01:11.144
SO, UM, OUR CAMPAIGN
ANNOUNCEMENT

01:11.144 --> 01:12.846
IS GONNA BE GREAT,
ISN'T IT?

01:12.846 --> 01:14.214
YES.

01:14.214 --> 01:15.616
RIGHT?
YES. YES.

01:15.616 --> 01:16.850
YES.

01:16.850 --> 01:19.953
ALL EYES ARE GONNA BE
ON THE FUTURE GOVERNOR

01:19.953 --> 01:23.389
AND HANDSOME
LIEUTENANT GOVERNOR.

01:23.389 --> 01:24.625
ALL RIGHT.

01:24.625 --> 01:27.160
GOOD.
[ SIGHS ]

01:28.662 --> 01:30.496
I KNOW
YOU FIND ME ATTRACTIVE.

01:32.633 --> 01:34.501
COME ON.
YOU DO, DON'T YOU?

01:34.501 --> 01:38.338
MY WIFE
IS VERY ATTRACTIVE.

01:38.338 --> 01:41.407
YES,
BUT SHE'S NOT HERE.

01:41.407 --> 01:44.144
NO, SHE'S NOT.

01:44.144 --> 01:49.182
AND YOU ARE HERE, ALONE,
IN A HOTEL ROOM.

01:49.182 --> 01:52.653
DAVID,
WHAT'S GOING ON?

01:55.355 --> 01:57.891
WHAT ARE YOU
FIGHTING ABOUT?

01:57.891 --> 02:00.366
IT'S A PERSONAL MATTER.

02:02.235 --> 02:03.637
[ CHUCKLES ]

02:03.637 --> 02:05.639
I BET IT'S SOMETHING
SHE DID.

02:07.741 --> 02:09.275
WHY WOULD YOU SAY THAT?

02:09.275 --> 02:11.377
BECAUSE YOU'RE MALLEABLE.

02:13.046 --> 02:16.716
YOU ALWAYS CONFORM
TO MAKE HER HAPPY.

02:16.716 --> 02:18.084
HMM.

02:18.084 --> 02:20.721
I USED TO BE THAT WAY
ONCE, TOO.

02:20.721 --> 02:24.024
I ACTUALLY
ALMOST MARRIED THE GUY.

02:24.024 --> 02:27.227
EVERY DAY
I'D WAKE UP SO ANGRY.

02:27.227 --> 02:29.495
AND, YOU KNOW,
I REALIZED IT WAS BECAUSE

02:29.495 --> 02:34.067
I WOULD ALWAYS GIVE
AND HE WOULD ONLY TAKE.

02:35.502 --> 02:38.338
I'M GLAD I GOT OUT.

02:38.338 --> 02:40.607
BUT I SEE
THAT YOU DIDN'T.

02:44.277 --> 02:45.879
YOU'RE WRONG ABOUT THAT.

02:45.879 --> 02:49.783
NO, I'M NOT.

02:49.783 --> 02:52.318
MY WIFE
IS A WONDERFUL WOMAN.

02:52.318 --> 02:54.588
I DIDN'T SAY
THAT SHE WASN'T.

02:54.588 --> 02:57.190
I SAID
THAT YOU WERE THE GIVER,

02:57.190 --> 03:00.400
THE ONE WHO ALWAYS COMPROMISES
AND GIVES IN.

03:03.403 --> 03:06.306
IT'S EXHAUSTING,
ISN'T IT?

03:11.011 --> 03:14.581
YOU DON'T KNOW
MY SITUATION.

03:18.919 --> 03:21.755
IT'S EXHAUSTING,
ISN'T IT?

03:24.558 --> 03:27.828
IT CAN BE.

03:27.828 --> 03:30.463
YEAH.

03:30.463 --> 03:33.033
THAT'S WHY
I DIDN'T MARRY HIM.

03:33.033 --> 03:35.435
I DIDN'T WANT
TO END UP LIKE THAT.

03:37.838 --> 03:40.507
I AM TIRED.

03:40.507 --> 03:42.008
WE SHOULD BOTH
GET SOME REST.

03:42.008 --> 03:43.777
YOU KNOW?

03:43.777 --> 03:44.845
YOU SURE
YOU DON'T WANT TO COME IN?

03:44.845 --> 03:47.313
YOU KNOW WE HAVE
THE ADJOINING DOOR.

03:47.313 --> 03:49.182
MM, YES.
YOU TOLD ME.

03:49.182 --> 03:50.216
[ CHUCKLES ]

03:50.216 --> 03:51.952
I'LL LEAVE MINE UNLOCKED.

03:51.952 --> 03:54.821
NO NEED FOR THAT.

03:55.956 --> 03:56.990
MAGGIE.

04:00.867 --> 04:04.370
[ DOOR UNLOCKS, OPENS ]

04:04.370 --> 04:05.572
GOOD NIGHT, MAGGIE.

04:05.572 --> 04:07.808
GOOD NIGHT.

04:11.177 --> 04:13.113
THANK YOU.

04:13.113 --> 04:14.180
[ CHUCKLES ]

04:20.887 --> 04:23.890
