05:01.635 --> 05:03.737
[ LOCK CLICKS ]

05:15.415 --> 05:19.119
[ Dialing ]

05:19.119 --> 05:22.556
[ Cellphone ringing ]

05:22.556 --> 05:23.857
VERONICA.

05:25.759 --> 05:29.095
I'M IN BED, DAVID.
WHAT DO YOU WANT?

05:30.864 --> 05:32.733
I WANT TO COME HOME.

05:32.733 --> 05:35.401
THEN DO IT.

05:35.401 --> 05:39.806
I NEED YOU TO TELL ME
WHERE JEFFERY'S CAR IS FIRST.

05:41.474 --> 05:43.309
I CAN'T TELL YOU THAT.

05:46.212 --> 05:50.784
HONEY, JUST TELL ME
WHERE THE CAR IS, PLEASE.

05:52.853 --> 05:56.523
I'M IN BED.
GOOD NIGHT.

05:56.523 --> 05:58.124
Veronica.

05:58.124 --> 05:59.993
WHAT?

05:59.993 --> 06:03.336
YOU NEED TO STOP THIS.

06:05.906 --> 06:08.408
DON'T MAKE ME HANG UP
ON YOU, DAVID.

06:09.610 --> 06:11.411
I SAID, "GOOD NIGHT."

06:19.786 --> 06:21.454
[ SIGHS ]

06:45.411 --> 06:48.348
WHERE DID YOU LEARN
HOW TO COOK LIKE THAT?

06:48.348 --> 06:49.550
COLIN INSTITUTE.

06:49.550 --> 06:53.319
MM‐HMM.
IT WAS REALLY GOOD.

06:53.319 --> 06:56.356
THANKS.

06:58.825 --> 07:01.067
SHE MIGHT NOT
COME BACK TONIGHT.

07:01.067 --> 07:03.737
WHY? SHE ON THE RUN
FROM SOMEBODY?

07:03.737 --> 07:08.108
NO. CANDACE ISN'T AFRAID
OF ANYBODY.

07:08.108 --> 07:11.044
THAT'S GOOD.

07:11.044 --> 07:12.045
THAT'S MY GIRL.

07:12.045 --> 07:14.715
YEAH.

07:14.715 --> 07:17.518
I LOVE HER SO MUCH.

07:17.518 --> 07:20.186
SHE'S SO TOUGH.

07:20.186 --> 07:22.355
IS THAT RIGHT?

07:22.355 --> 07:24.591
YEP.

07:24.591 --> 07:27.460
AND SHE'S SO SMART.

07:27.460 --> 07:29.362
IS SHE?

07:29.362 --> 07:30.931
YEAH.

07:30.931 --> 07:33.266
SHE'S HELPING ME
SUE MY PARENTS.

07:33.266 --> 07:35.035
SUE YOUR PARENTS?

07:35.035 --> 07:37.704
YEAH, FOR MY INHERITANCE.

07:37.704 --> 07:39.873
OH, YEAH?

07:39.873 --> 07:41.374
YEP.

07:41.374 --> 07:44.711
SHE'S GONNA BE
A GOOD LAWYER.

07:44.711 --> 07:47.948
THAT'S GOOD.
THAT'S GOOD TO KNOW.

07:47.948 --> 07:49.482
YEAH.

07:49.482 --> 07:51.384
SO, YOU'RE SUING
YOUR PARENTS?

07:51.384 --> 07:52.418
[ SIGHS ]

07:52.418 --> 07:55.121
THEY WON'T GIVE ME
MY INHERITANCE.

07:55.121 --> 07:57.457
HOW MUCH IS IT?

07:57.457 --> 08:00.661
$12 MILLION.

08:00.661 --> 08:03.904
CANDACE IS GONNA HELP ME
GET IT.

08:03.904 --> 08:06.472
IS THAT SO?

08:06.472 --> 08:08.609
MM‐HMM.

08:08.609 --> 08:10.911
YEAH.

08:10.911 --> 08:11.912
[ SIGHS ]

08:11.912 --> 08:14.247
THAT WINE WENT
TO MY HEAD.

08:14.247 --> 08:15.982
OH, YOU A LIGHTWEIGHT.

08:15.982 --> 08:19.052
I'M NOT
SUPPOSED TO DRINK.

08:19.052 --> 08:20.320
WHY NOT?

08:20.320 --> 08:22.422
JUST NOT SUPPOSED TO.

08:22.422 --> 08:23.790
SAYS WHO?

08:23.790 --> 08:25.792
MY DOCTOR, OKAY?

08:25.792 --> 08:27.327
DOCTOR?

08:27.327 --> 08:29.229
YEAH.

08:29.229 --> 08:30.864
WHAT'S WRONG WITH YOU?

08:30.864 --> 08:32.699
NOTHING.

08:32.699 --> 08:35.736
I JUST TAKE MEDICATIONS

08:35.736 --> 08:40.273
YOU'RE NOT SUPPOSED TO...
MIX WITH ALCOHOL.

08:42.475 --> 08:44.344
WELL, YOU DID IT.

08:44.344 --> 08:47.881
[ CHUCKLES ]
I DID, DIDN'T I?

08:47.881 --> 08:51.117
GOD, I FEEL STRANGE.
IS IT HOT IN HERE?

08:51.117 --> 08:53.787
OH, YEAH.

08:53.787 --> 08:56.156
OKAY.
I'M GONNA TURN THE AIR UP.

08:56.156 --> 08:58.424
OKAY.

09:09.142 --> 09:10.544
[ SIGHS ]

09:10.544 --> 09:11.878
YOU HAVE A NICE ASS.

09:11.878 --> 09:13.213
WHAT?

09:13.213 --> 09:15.816
YOUR ASS.
IT'S NICE.

09:15.816 --> 09:18.719
ALL THOSE YEARS
OF DANCING.

09:18.719 --> 09:19.753
YOU STRIP?

09:19.753 --> 09:22.856
NO, SILLY.
BALLET.

09:22.856 --> 09:25.526
OH.
WELL, IT WORKED FOR YOU.

09:25.526 --> 09:27.994
THANKS.

09:27.994 --> 09:31.665
I WISH CANDACE WOULD
HAVE TOLD ME ABOUT YOU.

09:31.665 --> 09:33.033
YOU'RE SO COOL.

09:33.033 --> 09:34.234
AND YOU'RE DRUNK.

09:34.234 --> 09:37.771
[ CHUCKLES ]
TIPSY.

09:37.771 --> 09:40.541
SO, WHERE HAVE YOU BEEN
FOR THE PAST THREE YEARS?

09:40.541 --> 09:42.876
I WAS IN PRISON.

09:42.876 --> 09:44.110
FOR WHAT?

09:44.110 --> 09:46.279
MURDER.

09:46.279 --> 09:48.214
REALLY?

09:48.214 --> 09:50.617
YEAH.
DOES THAT SCARE YOU?

09:50.617 --> 09:53.854
ARE YOU GONNA KILL ME?

09:53.854 --> 09:56.356
DO YOU WANT ME TO?

09:56.356 --> 10:00.534
NO.
BUT I WANT TO KILL SOMEONE.

10:00.534 --> 10:02.903
DO YOU?

10:02.903 --> 10:05.071
YEAH.

10:05.071 --> 10:06.773
WHO?

10:06.773 --> 10:10.010
MY PARENTS
AND MY BROTHER.

10:10.010 --> 10:11.812
OH, YEAH?

10:11.812 --> 10:14.815
YEAH.

10:14.815 --> 10:16.717
I BOUGHT A GUN
AND EVERYTHING.

10:16.717 --> 10:18.051
YOU WANT TO SEE IT?

10:18.051 --> 10:20.253
SURE.

10:20.253 --> 10:22.956
OKAY.
STAY HERE.

10:22.956 --> 10:25.025
STAY.

10:32.165 --> 10:33.667
[ CHUCKLES ]

10:37.571 --> 10:39.506
HOLD UP NOW.
WATCH THE TRIGGER.

10:39.506 --> 10:40.541
OH.

10:40.541 --> 10:42.342
WHOOPS.

10:42.342 --> 10:45.145
YO, WHY YOU WANT
TO KILL THEM?

10:46.446 --> 10:49.282
MY MOTHER'S A SPY.

10:49.282 --> 10:51.985
MY FATHER'S
A RETIRED BATTLED WARRIOR.

10:54.087 --> 10:56.389
DO YOU LIKE MY GUN?

10:57.958 --> 10:59.059
YEAH.

10:59.059 --> 11:02.435
HMM.
IT'S CUTE.

11:02.435 --> 11:03.904
YOU KNOW HOW TO USE IT?

11:03.904 --> 11:06.306
NO.

11:06.306 --> 11:08.474
YOU WANT ME TO SHOW YOU?

11:08.474 --> 11:10.577
PLEASE.

11:14.180 --> 11:15.816
FIRST
YOU LOAD IT LIKE THIS.

11:15.816 --> 11:18.484
MM‐HMM.

11:18.484 --> 11:20.286
TAKE IT IN YOUR HANDS.

11:20.286 --> 11:21.788
LIKE THIS?

11:21.788 --> 11:24.925
YEAH.
YOU FEEL THAT?

11:24.925 --> 11:27.260
MM‐HMM.
IT'S POWERFUL.

11:29.495 --> 11:30.931
AND IT'S HARD.

11:30.931 --> 11:32.398
STEEL.

11:36.002 --> 11:38.304
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

11:38.304 --> 11:39.640
YOU'RE BEAUTIFUL.

11:39.640 --> 11:41.007
STOP.
NO.

11:41.007 --> 11:42.643
STOP!
NO.

11:42.643 --> 11:44.044
STOP!

11:46.547 --> 11:49.149
[ CHUCKLES ] WHAT,
ARE YOU GONNA SHOOT ME?

11:51.552 --> 11:53.286
I THINK YOU'D BETTER GO.

11:55.889 --> 11:57.323
DO IT.

11:58.992 --> 12:00.967
YOU NEED TO GO.

12:00.967 --> 12:03.036
ARE YOU SURE?

12:03.036 --> 12:04.705
SWEET AMANDA?

12:04.705 --> 12:06.773
GO.

12:06.773 --> 12:07.774
NOW!

12:09.743 --> 12:11.678
OKAY.

12:11.678 --> 12:14.014
I'LL LEAVE.

12:14.014 --> 12:17.718
BUT IF CANDY SHOWS,
CALL ME.

12:19.720 --> 12:21.054
I'LL WRITE MY NUMBER DOWN.

12:22.789 --> 12:26.192
AND IF SHE DOESN'T SHOW
AND YOU WANT TO HANG...

12:26.192 --> 12:27.861
CALL ME.

12:29.462 --> 12:32.498
AND I'LL REALLY SHOW YOU
WANT TO DO WITH A LOADED GUN.

12:48.414 --> 12:51.451
[ DOOR OPENS, CLOSES ]

12:58.024 --> 13:00.293
[ CRICKETS CHIRPING ]

13:00.293 --> 13:02.335
IS HE HERE?
IS HE HOME?

13:02.335 --> 13:03.403
NO.

13:03.403 --> 13:04.404
AND I'VE BEEN DRIVING AROUND
FOR HOURS.

13:04.404 --> 13:05.471
DAMN IT, KATHERYN,

13:05.471 --> 13:06.873
HOW COULD YOU LET HIM
OUT OF YOUR SIGHT?

13:06.873 --> 13:08.742
HE'S A GROWN MAN, JIM.
HE'S NOT 2.

13:08.742 --> 13:10.176
I KNOW THAT.

13:10.176 --> 13:12.245
WHERE CAN HE BE?

13:12.245 --> 13:14.414
HE WAS AT THE GRAVE SITE.

13:14.414 --> 13:15.916
WHOSE GRAVE SITE?

13:15.916 --> 13:17.083
WHOSE GRAVE SITE
DO YOU THINK?

13:17.083 --> 13:18.519
THE LITTLE GIRL'S GRAVE SITE,
KATHERYN.

13:18.519 --> 13:19.553
WHAT?
YES.

13:19.553 --> 13:20.721
[ SIGHS ]

13:20.721 --> 13:22.422
HER MOTHER WAS THERE,
HER GRANDFATHER WAS THERE.

13:22.422 --> 13:23.423
THEY RECOGNIZED HIM.

13:23.423 --> 13:24.525
HOW DO YOU KNOW THIS?

13:24.525 --> 13:25.726
I KNOW A LOT OF THINGS,
KATHERYN.

13:25.726 --> 13:27.427
I TOLD YOU.
I AM HANDLING THIS.

13:27.427 --> 13:29.262
I ASKED YOU TO DO
ONE SIMPLE THING.

13:29.262 --> 13:30.531
I CAN'T DO IT ALL MYSELF.

13:30.531 --> 13:32.032
I DIDN'T KNOW
HE WAS GONE.

13:32.032 --> 13:33.099
OBVIOUSLY.

13:33.099 --> 13:34.167
WELL,
DID YOU FIND AMANDA?

13:34.167 --> 13:35.168
I WAS ON MY WAY TO SEE HER

13:35.168 --> 13:36.336
WHEN THIS THING
WITH WYATT HAPPENED.

13:36.336 --> 13:37.971
SHE'S NOT ANSWERING
OUR CALLS.

13:37.971 --> 13:40.406
I'LL GO GET HER AND
I'LL BRING HER HOME TOMORROW.

13:40.406 --> 13:41.942
SHE SHOULDN'T BE HERE, JIM.

13:41.942 --> 13:44.477
I AM NOT HAVING
THIS CONVERSATION WITH YOU

13:44.477 --> 13:45.779
AGAIN EVER.

13:45.779 --> 13:47.313
EVER.

13:49.282 --> 13:51.051
WYATT.

13:51.051 --> 13:52.519
[ GASPS ]

13:52.519 --> 13:53.554
COME HERE.

13:53.554 --> 13:55.756
DAD, I'M NOT HIGH.

13:55.756 --> 13:57.190
THANK GOD.

13:57.190 --> 13:59.693
I WENT TO HER GRAVE SITE.

13:59.693 --> 14:01.802
I KNOW.
DAMN IT, WYATT.

14:01.802 --> 14:03.570
HER MOM SAW ME THERE.

14:03.570 --> 14:05.305
HER GRANDFATHER, TOO.

14:05.305 --> 14:06.306
I KNOW THAT.

14:06.306 --> 14:08.241
WHAT THE HELL
WERE YOU THINKING?

14:08.241 --> 14:10.476
I'M SORRY, DAD.

14:10.476 --> 14:13.213
IT JUST REALLY HURTS.

14:13.213 --> 14:14.848
I UNDERSTAND.

14:14.848 --> 14:17.818
IT HURTS LIKE HELL THAT I ‐‐
I DID SOMETHING LIKE THAT.

14:17.818 --> 14:19.385
YOU WANT TO GO TO JAIL?

14:19.385 --> 14:21.221
NO?
NO, DAD.

14:21.221 --> 14:22.355
YOU SAW IT, RIGHT?

14:22.355 --> 14:24.424
YOU SAW HOW BAD
IT WAS IN THERE.

14:24.424 --> 14:25.892
YEAH.

14:25.892 --> 14:27.961
BUT IF YOU FEEL SO AWFUL THAT
YOU WANT TO GO BACK TO JAIL,

14:27.961 --> 14:28.962
YOU WANT TO COP
TO THIS WHOLE THING,

14:28.962 --> 14:29.996
YOU JUST TELL ME, SON,

14:29.996 --> 14:31.031
AND I'LL TAKE YOU THERE
RIGHT NOW.

14:31.031 --> 14:32.065
LET'S GO.
COME ON.

14:32.065 --> 14:33.800
NO.

14:33.800 --> 14:34.868
NO?

14:34.868 --> 14:36.002
I DON'T WANT TO GO
THERE AGAIN, DAD.

14:36.002 --> 14:37.938
THEN YOU HAVE
GOT TO FIGURE OUT

14:37.938 --> 14:40.073
A BETTER WAY
TO HANDLE THIS, WYATT.

14:40.073 --> 14:42.208
NOW, MY ASS IS HANGING OUT
TO DRY, TOO,

14:42.208 --> 14:44.778
AND I'M DOING THE BEST
THAT I CAN TO COVER YOURS.

14:44.778 --> 14:46.046
BUT I CAN'T DO IT ALONE.

14:46.046 --> 14:47.781
YOU'RE GONNA HAVE TO
LET THIS GO.

14:47.781 --> 14:50.651
I'M TRYING, DAD.
IT'S JUST HARD.

14:50.651 --> 14:54.420
WE'RE BOTH IN THIS
WITH YOU TOGETHER.

14:54.420 --> 14:58.191
MOM, YOU DIDN'T DO ANYTHING.
I DID.

14:58.191 --> 14:59.826
I KNOW, HONEY.

14:59.826 --> 15:01.702
I DID THIS, DAD.
WYATT, WYATT, WYATT, WYATT.

15:01.702 --> 15:04.137
HOLD IT TOGETHER.

15:04.137 --> 15:06.306
DON'T GET HYSTERICAL.

15:06.306 --> 15:09.776
COME ON. MAN UP.

15:09.776 --> 15:12.345
SO WHAT ARE WE GONNA DO
ABOUT HER SEEING ME?

15:12.345 --> 15:13.346
I'VE GOT THAT
UNDER CONTROL.

15:13.346 --> 15:14.480
IT'S ALL HANDLED.

15:14.480 --> 15:16.082
YOU DON'T HAVE TO WORRY
ABOUT THAT.

15:18.084 --> 15:20.521
I JUST WANT TO GO AWAY.

15:24.525 --> 15:26.727
WHERE?

15:26.727 --> 15:29.395
ANYWHERE.

15:29.395 --> 15:32.966
COULD WE GO TO THE MOUNTAINS
FOR AWHILE OR SOMETHING?

15:32.966 --> 15:35.068
SURE.

15:35.068 --> 15:36.803
I'LL GET YOUR SISTER.

15:36.803 --> 15:39.372
WE'LL ALL GO
TO THE MOUNTAINS.

15:39.372 --> 15:40.674
OKAY?

15:40.674 --> 15:43.877
CAN YOU, PLEASE?

15:43.877 --> 15:46.279
YES.

15:46.279 --> 15:48.014
I CAN'T DO IT THIS WEEK.

15:48.014 --> 15:50.316
JUST HANG IN
FOR A COUPLE DAYS, OKAY?

15:50.316 --> 15:51.552
TILL I ANNOUNCE
I'M RUNNING.

15:53.687 --> 15:55.088
YOU'RE STILL GONNA RUN?

15:55.088 --> 15:57.958
YES. OF COURSE
I'M STILL GONNA RUN.

16:00.834 --> 16:02.235
OKAY.

16:02.235 --> 16:03.937
I'LL GO WITH YOU, WYATT.

16:03.937 --> 16:05.639
WE CAN LEAVE RIGHT NOW.

16:07.440 --> 16:09.409
I JUST WANT TO GO WITH DAD.

16:11.211 --> 16:12.713
OKAY.

16:12.713 --> 16:13.847
I'M GONNA GO LAY DOWN.

16:13.847 --> 16:15.148
HEY, HEY.
I LOVE YOU.

16:20.420 --> 16:21.555
LOVE YOU.

16:21.555 --> 16:23.356
YOU TOO, MOM.

16:28.695 --> 16:30.363
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

16:30.363 --> 16:32.432
IS HE GONNA MAKE IT?

16:32.432 --> 16:34.500
YEAH,
HE'S GONNA MAKE IT.

16:34.500 --> 16:36.302
WE'RE ALL GONNA MAKE IT.

16:47.981 --> 16:49.382
YOU SURE IT WAS HIM?

16:49.382 --> 16:52.653
YES. IT WAS THE SAME GUY
THAT THEY ARRESTED.

16:52.653 --> 16:55.188
I SAW HIM
IN THE INTERROGATION ROOM.

16:55.188 --> 16:58.224
WE WERE WAITING
ON MY DAUGHTER TO I. D. HIM,

16:58.224 --> 16:59.893
BUT SHE NEVER SHOWED UP.

16:59.893 --> 17:02.936
THEN HE WAS
AT LIZZIE'S GRAVE SITE.

17:02.936 --> 17:05.939
WHY WOULD WYATT CRYER GO
TO HER GRAVE SITE?

17:05.939 --> 17:07.974
GUILT.

17:07.974 --> 17:10.443
YOU HAVE TO DO SOMETHING, BYRON.

17:10.443 --> 17:11.912
OKAY.

17:11.912 --> 17:13.079
WHAT ARE YOU GONNA DO?

17:13.079 --> 17:14.748
TALK TO THE D.A.
AFTER I LEAVE HERE.

17:14.748 --> 17:15.849
GOOD.

17:15.849 --> 17:17.150
THEY MAY WANT YOU
TO TESTIFY.

17:17.150 --> 17:19.653
YEAH, I WILL.
I WILL.

17:19.653 --> 17:20.854
OKAY. I GOT TO GO.

17:20.854 --> 17:22.488
OKAY.

17:22.488 --> 17:24.357
CALL YOU TOMORROW?

17:24.357 --> 17:25.592
THANK YOU.

17:25.592 --> 17:28.361
IT'S GOOD TO MEET YOU,
MICHAEL.

17:28.361 --> 17:29.596
LIKEWISE.

17:29.596 --> 17:30.997
I WISH IT WAS UNDER
BETTER CIRCUMSTANCES.

17:30.997 --> 17:33.466
YEAH, ME TOO.

17:33.466 --> 17:34.635
SEE YOU LATER, BYRON.

17:43.343 --> 17:45.145
HE'LL HANDLE IT.

17:45.145 --> 17:47.914
HOW COULD THIS ‐‐

17:47.914 --> 17:49.516
HOW COULD THIS MAN
JUST WALK LIKE THAT?

17:49.516 --> 17:52.252
I DON'T KNOW.

17:52.252 --> 17:54.087
HIS FATHER IS CRAZY.

17:55.789 --> 17:58.058
IT'S LATE.
I'M KEEPING YOU UP.

17:58.058 --> 18:00.193
NO.
ACTUALLY, I'M FINE.

18:00.193 --> 18:01.467
NO, I‐I SHOULD GO.

18:01.467 --> 18:03.069
I NEED TO CHECK ON TINA.

18:03.069 --> 18:04.337
HOW IS SHE?

18:04.337 --> 18:05.471
[ SIGHS ]

18:07.207 --> 18:08.509
I WISH
I COULD GET HER CLEAN.

18:08.509 --> 18:10.410
OH.

18:10.410 --> 18:12.378
THAT'S HARD.

18:12.378 --> 18:14.080
WHAT YOU KNOW ABOUT IT?

18:14.080 --> 18:17.518
I HAD A SISTER
WHO WAS ADDICTED TO CRACK.

18:17.518 --> 18:18.752
MM.

18:18.752 --> 18:20.954
SHE DIED.

18:20.954 --> 18:23.423
I WORRY ABOUT MY DAUGHTER
EVERY DAY.

18:23.423 --> 18:25.592
I UNDERSTAND THAT.

18:25.592 --> 18:28.562
I'M GLAD YOUR SON
IS BETTER.

18:28.562 --> 18:29.596
COME ON.
WALK ME OUT.

18:29.596 --> 18:30.631
YEAH.

18:41.107 --> 18:44.144
THAT IS GOOD NEWS
ABOUT YOUR SON.

18:44.144 --> 18:46.713
YES, IT IS REALLY GOOD.

18:46.713 --> 18:48.281
AND HE'S DOING
REAL GOOD, TOO.

18:48.281 --> 18:51.451
MM, MM, MM.
[ LAUGHS ]

18:51.451 --> 18:53.854
OOH, THAT POOR DOCTOR
IS IN SHOCK, THOUGH.

18:53.854 --> 18:56.590
HE'S CALLING IT A MIRACLE.

18:56.590 --> 18:58.424
THAT IS WONDERFUL,
HANNA.

18:58.424 --> 19:00.360
YEAH.
MM.

19:00.360 --> 19:02.402
GOD IS SO GOOD,
MICHAEL.

19:02.402 --> 19:04.738
YES, HE IS.
MM‐HMM.

19:04.738 --> 19:05.772
HEY, DID YOU TELL HIM

19:05.772 --> 19:06.873
THAT I WAS SORRY
FOR CUTTING HIS GRASS?

19:06.873 --> 19:07.908
[ Chuckling ] NO.
NOT YET.

19:07.908 --> 19:09.075
ALL RIGHT.

19:09.075 --> 19:11.277
I'M GONNA LET YOU
TELL HIM THAT YOURSELF.

19:11.277 --> 19:13.213
LISTEN.
HMM?

19:13.213 --> 19:15.315
I'M GONNA HAVE A SURPRISE PARTY
FOR HIM WHEN HE GETS OUT.

19:15.315 --> 19:17.217
RIGHT.
YOU SHOULD COME.

19:17.217 --> 19:20.453
OH, I'D LOVE TO.
I'D LOVE TO.

19:20.453 --> 19:22.088
OKAY.

19:22.088 --> 19:24.290
[ SIGHS ]
I'M GONNA GO, ALL RIGHT?

19:24.290 --> 19:25.626
LET YOU GET SOME SLEEP.

19:25.626 --> 19:28.228
OKAY.

19:28.228 --> 19:29.796
ALL RIGHT.

19:29.796 --> 19:31.732
I'LL SEE YOU LATER?

19:31.732 --> 19:33.433
I'LL SEE YOU LATER.

19:33.433 --> 19:34.668
[ CHUCKLES ]

19:46.046 --> 19:47.480
WHAT IS IT?

19:54.755 --> 19:57.558
MNH, MNH.

19:57.558 --> 19:59.826
WHAT ARE YOU DOING,
MICHAEL?

19:59.826 --> 20:02.603
YOU'RE A BEAUTIFUL WOMAN,
HANNA.

20:05.105 --> 20:07.307
I KNOW IT'S TIME
FOR YOU TO GO.

20:07.307 --> 20:10.276
[ SIGHS ]

20:10.276 --> 20:12.078
I'M SORRY.
I'M SORRY.

20:12.078 --> 20:14.615
I ‐‐ I'M JUST DEALING
WITH A LOT.

20:14.615 --> 20:16.917
I CAN UNDERSTAND THAT.

20:18.184 --> 20:19.786
I'LL SEE YOU LATER.

20:19.786 --> 20:23.156
OKAY.
BYE.

20:23.156 --> 20:24.525
BYE.

20:36.770 --> 20:39.405
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

20:55.188 --> 20:57.190
[ CRICKETS CHIRPING ]

21:51.552 --> 21:54.387
DAVID.

21:56.890 --> 21:59.392
I KNOW YOU DON'T THINK
YOU'RE STAYING IN THIS BED.

22:15.315 --> 22:17.718
GO ON NOW.

22:17.718 --> 22:20.587
GO ON. [ LAUGHS ]

22:20.587 --> 22:23.056
DAVID, MOVE.

22:25.391 --> 22:27.427
[ GASPS ]

22:27.427 --> 22:29.162
WHAT ARE YOU DOING
IN MY HOUSE?

22:29.162 --> 22:31.665
I CAN'T FIND CANDY.

22:31.665 --> 22:33.567
GET OUT OF HERE!

22:33.567 --> 22:36.903
WHAT ARE YOU GONNA DO?
SCREAM?

22:36.903 --> 22:39.239
NO.
GET OUT OF MY HOUSE!

22:39.239 --> 22:40.306
YOU WANT ME, DON'T YOU?

22:40.306 --> 22:43.309
I WANT YOU
OUT OF MY HOUSE.

22:43.309 --> 22:45.178
I SAW YOUR MAN ON TV.

22:45.178 --> 22:48.048
I WANT YOU
OUT OF MY HOUSE.

22:50.450 --> 22:52.953
BORING.

22:52.953 --> 22:54.888
YOU SHOULD LET ME PUT THEM LEGS
IN THE AIR.

22:54.888 --> 22:56.957
I CAN GIVE YOU
WHAT YOU'RE REALLY MISSING.

22:56.957 --> 22:58.659
I'M GONNA TELL YOU
ONE MORE TIME.

22:58.659 --> 23:02.603
WHEN YOU SAW ME,
I KNOW YOU WANTED ME.

23:02.603 --> 23:03.937
KISS ME.

23:03.937 --> 23:05.105
BOY!

23:06.607 --> 23:07.608
YOU WANT ME?

23:07.608 --> 23:09.543
YOU THINK
I'M PLAYING WITH YOU?

23:09.543 --> 23:10.644
YOU'RE NOT SCARED?

23:10.644 --> 23:14.548
HELL NO.
YOU DON'T SCARE ME.

23:14.548 --> 23:16.382
YOU SHOULD BE.

23:16.382 --> 23:18.451
WHAT YOU GONNA DO, HUH?

23:18.451 --> 23:21.988
YOU GONNA RAPE ME?
HMM?

23:21.988 --> 23:23.990
YOU GONNA HIT ME?

23:23.990 --> 23:26.359
HMM?

23:28.161 --> 23:30.263
YOU'RE FUNNY.

23:30.263 --> 23:32.966
WHATEVER YOU THINK
YOU CAME IN HERE TO DO,

23:32.966 --> 23:36.870
IT WILL BE THE LAST THING
YOU DO TO ANYONE.

23:36.870 --> 23:38.605
I CAN'T FIND CANDY.

23:38.605 --> 23:40.173
WHY NOT?
I GAVE YOU HER ADDRESS.

23:40.173 --> 23:41.775
I GAVE YOU
HER MOTHER'S ADDRESS.

23:41.775 --> 23:44.077
WHAT DO YOU NEED, A MAP?
ARE YOU THAT WEAK, QUINCY?

23:44.077 --> 23:45.445
DON'T CALL ME WEAK.

23:45.445 --> 23:46.980
GET YOUR DAMN HANDS
OUT OF MY FACE.

23:46.980 --> 23:47.981
YOU CAN'T FIND HER.

23:47.981 --> 23:49.449
SHE'S NOT WHERE
YOU'D SAID SHE'D BE.

23:49.449 --> 23:51.151
THEN FIND HER!

23:51.151 --> 23:53.319
AND GET OUT OF HERE!

23:54.988 --> 23:56.890
YOU STINK.

23:59.259 --> 24:00.901
AND YOU'RE WET.

24:00.901 --> 24:03.269
GET OUT.

24:03.269 --> 24:06.406
[ SCOFFS ]
YOU LIKE THAT THUG LIFE.

24:06.406 --> 24:09.109
[ SCOFFS ]
YEAH.

24:09.109 --> 24:12.779
I PUT GUYS LIKE YOU AWAY
FOR LIFE.

24:12.779 --> 24:15.549
YOU GOT ME OUT IN A DAY,
THOUGH.

24:15.549 --> 24:16.583
I NEED TO REPAY YOU.

24:16.583 --> 24:17.818
I WILL PAY YOU

24:17.818 --> 24:20.320
BY PUTTING YOU BACK IN JAIL
WITHIN AN HOUR.

24:20.320 --> 24:21.487
NOW GET OUT OF HERE

24:21.487 --> 24:23.924
AND DO WHAT THE HELL
I SET YOU FREE TO DO.

24:23.924 --> 24:29.229
STINKING UP MY $1,200 SHEETS
WITH YOUR THUG‐ASS MESS.

24:29.229 --> 24:30.797
GET OUT OF MY DAMN HOUSE.

24:32.132 --> 24:33.499
YOU REALLY ARE
NOT AFRAID OF ME.

24:33.499 --> 24:34.801
IF YOU COME BACK HERE,

24:34.801 --> 24:37.671
THEY WILL BE ROLLING YOU
OUT OF HERE IN A BODY BAG.

24:39.105 --> 24:40.941
YES, MA'AM.

24:49.449 --> 24:50.851
IT'S A NICE PLACE.

24:50.851 --> 24:54.688
AND THIS IS THE LAST TIME
YOU WILL SEE IT.

25:01.702 --> 25:03.504
AND CLOSE
WHATEVER WINDOW

25:03.504 --> 25:05.672
YOUR SLIMY ASS
CRAWLED THROUGH.

25:07.941 --> 25:09.409
YOU REALLY
SHOULD LOCK THESE.

25:24.157 --> 25:25.926
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

25:54.555 --> 25:56.056
[ LAUGHS ]

25:56.056 --> 25:58.324
THIS HERE IS CRAZY.

25:58.324 --> 25:59.960
[ CHUCKLES ]

25:59.960 --> 26:01.401
OH, MY GOODNESS.

26:01.401 --> 26:03.303
UH, BOY,
I HAVE TO GO TO WORK.

26:03.303 --> 26:05.071
YOU GONNA LEAVE ME HERE
LIKE THIS?

26:05.071 --> 26:07.273
BYE, BENNY.

26:07.273 --> 26:10.110
NOW, YOU KNOW I'M GETTING
OUT OF HERE TOMORROW.

26:10.110 --> 26:11.778
SAYS WHO?
DOCTOR.

26:11.778 --> 26:13.379
YOU HAVEN'T GOTTEN OUT
OF THIS BED YET.

26:13.379 --> 26:14.815
[ SCOFFS ]
PLEASE. YES, I HAVE.

26:14.815 --> 26:16.316
NO, YOU HAVEN'T.

26:16.316 --> 26:20.153
MAN, JUST GIVE ME
YOUR NUMBER.

26:20.153 --> 26:22.422
FOR WHAT?

26:22.422 --> 26:23.957
'CAUSE I WANT
TO TAKE YOU OUT.

26:25.792 --> 26:27.628
REALLY?
MM‐HMM.

26:27.628 --> 26:29.596
WHY YOU ‐‐
WHY YOU LOOK SO SURPRISED?

26:29.596 --> 26:32.498
'CAUSE IN HIGH SCHOOL,

26:32.498 --> 26:35.068
YOU THOUGHT I WAS THE FAT GIRL
THAT NOBODY LIKED.

26:35.068 --> 26:37.604
THAT'S WHY
YOU FELT SORRY FOR ME.

26:37.604 --> 26:38.839
THAT'S NOT IT.

26:38.839 --> 26:40.306
THEN WHAT WAS IT?

26:40.306 --> 26:42.809
I THOUGHT YOU WERE CUTE.

26:42.809 --> 26:43.744
[ CHUCKLES ]

26:43.744 --> 26:46.747
BUT YOU WOULDN'T GO
OUT WITH ME.

26:46.747 --> 26:50.450
NO, BECAUSE
YOU WANTED KATHY.

26:50.450 --> 26:51.518
MAN, GO ON WITH THAT.

26:51.518 --> 26:53.153
GET OUT OF HERE
WITH THAT, MAN.

26:53.153 --> 26:54.154
REALLY?

26:54.154 --> 26:56.957
AND, UH, GAIL?
WAS THAT IT?

26:56.957 --> 26:58.892
WOW. GAIL.
MM‐HMM.

26:58.892 --> 27:00.801
[ Chuckling ] W‐WOW.

27:00.801 --> 27:04.905
SEE?
YOU WERE A FLIRT.

27:04.905 --> 27:08.141
AND, UH, AND A WHORE.

27:08.141 --> 27:09.710
[ SCOFFS ]
MM‐HMM.

27:09.710 --> 27:12.879
PLEASE.
I WAS NOT A WHORE, ALL RIGHT?

27:12.879 --> 27:16.382
SEE, THING ABOUT ME IS,
I WAS MORE OF A, UH...

27:16.382 --> 27:17.518
A WHORE.

27:17.518 --> 27:19.520
[ CHUCKLES ]
YEAH.

27:19.520 --> 27:21.454
AIN'T NO WAY TO TALK TO A MAN
THAT'S IN MY CONDITION.

27:21.454 --> 27:24.324
[ CHUCKLES ]
YOU SAID YOU WERE FINE.

27:24.324 --> 27:25.826
I AM.

27:25.826 --> 27:27.060
BYE, BENNY.

27:27.060 --> 27:29.295
SO YOU'RE REALLY NOT GONNA
GIVE ME YOUR NUMBER?

27:29.295 --> 27:31.898
WHY DON'T YOU
GIVE ME YOURS?

27:31.898 --> 27:33.567
I DON'T REMEMBER MY NUMBER.

27:33.567 --> 27:35.435
STOP LYING.

27:35.435 --> 27:36.637
NO, I HAD A HEAD TRAUMA.

27:36.637 --> 27:38.304
I DON'T REMEMBER NOTHING.
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

27:38.304 --> 27:41.908
FINE.

27:41.908 --> 27:43.209
[ SIGHS ]

27:46.880 --> 27:49.850
HERE'S MY NUMBER.
THANK YOU.

27:49.850 --> 27:51.652
BYE.

27:51.652 --> 27:53.520
SEE YA.

27:58.725 --> 27:59.860
HI, DARLENE.

27:59.860 --> 28:01.401
HI.

28:01.401 --> 28:03.469
HE DOESN'T REMEMBER
HIS NUMBER.

28:03.469 --> 28:04.771
Hanna: OH, HE DOESN'T?

28:04.771 --> 28:07.273
YEAH.
THAT'S WHAT HE SAID.

28:07.273 --> 28:08.942
[ LAUGHS ]

28:08.942 --> 28:10.143
I'LL SEE YOU LATER,
RIGHT?

28:10.143 --> 28:11.444
YES, MA'AM.

28:11.444 --> 28:13.413
THANK YOU, DARLENE.

28:13.413 --> 28:14.414
MM.

28:14.414 --> 28:16.449
[ BENNY LAUGHS ]

28:16.449 --> 28:19.786
I HEARD YOU CAN'T
REMEMBER YOUR NUMBER.

28:19.786 --> 28:21.522
SO WHAT IF I CAN'T?

28:21.522 --> 28:23.123
THEN YOU'LL JUST HAVE TO STAY
HERE A FEW MORE DAYS.

28:23.123 --> 28:26.627
MAN, I REMEMBER MY NUMBER.
I JUST WANTED HERS.

28:26.627 --> 28:28.361
SEE?
YOU BETTER STOP PLAYING.

28:28.361 --> 28:30.531
I'M JUST JOKING AROUND.
LIGHTEN UP.

28:30.531 --> 28:31.598
[ CHUCKLES ]

28:33.333 --> 28:36.336
ALL YOUR TEST RESULTS
ARE COMING BACK NORMAL.

28:36.336 --> 28:38.338
TOLD YOU, BRO.
I'M MADE OF STEEL, MAN.

28:38.338 --> 28:39.339
LOOK AT THAT.

28:39.339 --> 28:40.373
I'M STARTING
TO BELIEVE THAT.

28:40.373 --> 28:41.508
YEAH.
[ CHUCKLES ]

28:41.508 --> 28:43.944
I NEED ONE MORE TEST RESULT
I'M WAITING FOR.

28:43.944 --> 28:45.145
IT WILL BE BACK TOMORROW.

28:45.145 --> 28:46.279
AND THEN
I'LL GET YOU DISCHARGED.

28:46.279 --> 28:47.781
SO I GOT TO STAY HERE
FOR ANOTHER NIGHT?

28:47.781 --> 28:49.716
I'M SORRY.
MM.

28:49.716 --> 28:50.717
FINE.

28:50.717 --> 28:52.786
I'LL SEE YOU LATER.

28:52.786 --> 28:54.220
MISS YOUNG?

28:54.220 --> 28:56.056
YES?
HAVE A NICE DAY.

28:56.056 --> 28:58.024
THANK YOU, DOCTOR.
BYE.

28:58.024 --> 28:59.526
MM.

28:59.526 --> 29:00.794
I WANT
TO GET OUT OF HERE.

29:00.794 --> 29:02.368
I KNOW.
AND I WANT YOU OUT OF HERE.

29:02.368 --> 29:05.105
I WASHED YOUR BEDCLOTHES
AND YOUR SHEETS

29:05.105 --> 29:07.541
AND I WILL MAKE
YOUR FAVORITE MEAL.

29:07.541 --> 29:08.675
YOU CALL CANDACE?

29:08.675 --> 29:10.376
OHH.

29:10.376 --> 29:11.444
SHE'S NOT ANSWERING.

29:11.444 --> 29:13.213
YOU DIDN'T CALL HER,
DID YOU?

29:13.213 --> 29:14.314
NO, I DID.

29:14.314 --> 29:15.248
YOU LEAVE A VOICEMAIL?

29:15.248 --> 29:16.850
HER VOICEMAIL IS FULL.

29:16.850 --> 29:18.885
MAMA ‐‐

29:18.885 --> 29:20.887
WHAT? I‐IT WAS.

29:20.887 --> 29:22.022
CALL HER NOW.

29:23.524 --> 29:24.591
NOW?

29:24.591 --> 29:26.359
YEAH. 'CAUSE I KNOW
YOU DIDN'T CALL HER.

29:26.359 --> 29:27.761
YES, I DID.

29:27.761 --> 29:29.062
LET ME SEE.

29:29.062 --> 29:31.364
YOU KNOW WHAT, BENNY?

29:31.364 --> 29:33.233
MM, MM, MM.

29:33.233 --> 29:34.668
YOU WATCH.

29:34.668 --> 29:36.036
[ Dialing ]

29:38.605 --> 29:41.274
<i>THIS MAILBOX IS FULL</i>
<i>AND IS UNABLE TO...</i>

29:41.274 --> 29:43.476
SEE?
STRAIGHT TO VOICEMAIL.

29:43.476 --> 29:44.511
[ SIGHS ]

29:47.213 --> 29:48.715
WHEN'S THE LAST TIME
YOU TALKED TO HER?

29:48.715 --> 29:51.051
YOU KNOW I DON'T TALK
TO YOUR SISTER.

29:53.787 --> 29:55.689
THIS ‐‐
THIS ISN'T LIKE HER.

29:55.689 --> 29:57.223
LIKE, AT ALL.

29:57.223 --> 29:59.092
LISTEN.
CANDACE ‐‐

29:59.092 --> 30:01.702
M‐MAYBE I SHOULD JUST CALL HER
FROM MY PHONE.

30:01.702 --> 30:02.869
HERE IT IS.

30:02.869 --> 30:04.671
MM.

30:04.671 --> 30:05.739
[ Dialing ]

30:05.739 --> 30:08.108
WHEN'S THE LAST TIME
YOU TALKED TO HER?

30:08.108 --> 30:09.109
FOR REAL.

30:09.109 --> 30:12.278
LAST WEEK.

30:12.278 --> 30:15.281
<i>THIS MAILBOX IS FULL</i>
<i>AND IS UNABLE TO ACCEPT...</i>

30:15.281 --> 30:16.382
I DON'T LIKE THIS.

30:16.382 --> 30:18.218
BENNY, CANDACE IS GONNA
TAKE CARE OF CANDACE.

30:18.218 --> 30:19.520
[ Dialing ]

30:19.520 --> 30:21.855
YOU GOT TOO MUCH TO WORRY ABOUT
TO BE WORRYING ABOUT HER.

30:21.855 --> 30:24.525
IT'S MY SISTER, SO...

30:24.525 --> 30:26.660
AND YOU'VE BEEN OUT OF IT.

30:26.660 --> 30:28.194
[ BEEP ]

30:28.194 --> 30:29.996
NO ANSWER.

30:29.996 --> 30:31.665
I TOLD YOU.

30:31.665 --> 30:33.099
[ SIGHS ]

30:33.099 --> 30:35.301
BENNY, HAVE YOU TALKED TO HER
ABOUT HER BABY?

30:37.470 --> 30:38.972
SHE TOLD ME
SHE HAD A NANNY.

30:38.972 --> 30:40.173
I TOLD YOU THAT ALREADY.

30:40.173 --> 30:41.742
I KNOW.
YEAH, YOU TOLD ME.

30:41.742 --> 30:43.076
THAT'S ALL SHE TOLD ME,
SO...

30:43.076 --> 30:46.046
WELL, CAN YOU REMEMBER
ANYTHING ELSE?

30:49.950 --> 30:51.552
UM, ACTUALLY,
I REMEMBER EVERYTHING.

30:51.552 --> 30:52.819
WELL, GOOD.

30:52.819 --> 30:55.355
DO YOU REMEMBER HER SAYING
ANYTHING ABOUT YOUR NEPHEW?

30:55.355 --> 30:58.491
THAT'S ALL SHE SAID
ABOUT HER BABY, BUT...

30:58.491 --> 31:01.602
[ GRUNTS ]

31:01.602 --> 31:04.571
...I REMEMBER EVERYTHING
YOU SAID ABOUT YOUR BABY.

31:04.571 --> 31:06.439
BENNY...

31:08.742 --> 31:11.311
YOU WANT TO TALK ABOUT WHAT
HAPPENED THE DAY I GOT HIT?

31:11.311 --> 31:14.648
WHAT HAPPENED?

31:14.648 --> 31:17.083
DO YOU ‐‐ YOU REMEMBER
WHO WAS DRIVING?

31:17.083 --> 31:18.118
I DON'T KNOW.

31:18.118 --> 31:20.420
ALL I REMEMBER
IS BRIGHT LIGHTS,

31:20.420 --> 31:23.223
BUT I REMEMBER EVERYTHING
THAT HAPPENED,

31:23.223 --> 31:25.291
YOU KNOW,
BEFORE I GOT HIT.

31:25.291 --> 31:27.928
YOU KNOW,
AROUND THE TABLE AT HOME.

31:27.928 --> 31:29.229
AH.

31:31.497 --> 31:33.967
DO YOU?

31:33.967 --> 31:38.705
HOW COME YOU DIDN'T TELL ME
THAT MR. WATSON WAS MY FATHER?

31:40.574 --> 31:42.242
BENNY, I WANTED TO.

31:42.242 --> 31:44.511
OH.

31:44.511 --> 31:47.748
[ CHUCKLES ]

31:47.748 --> 31:49.750
IT'S JUST A LITTLE,
LITTLE MESSED UP

31:49.750 --> 31:50.951
I FOUND OUT LIKE THAT.

31:50.951 --> 31:53.119
I KNOW THAT, BABY.
I'M SORRY.

31:53.119 --> 31:56.957
I SHOULD HAVE TOLD YOU.

31:59.760 --> 32:00.934
YOU KNOW WHAT?

32:00.934 --> 32:02.468
I THINK I'M GONNA ‐‐

32:02.468 --> 32:03.870
I THINK I'M GONNA
GIVE HIM A CALL.

32:03.870 --> 32:06.139
MM.

32:06.139 --> 32:08.274
YEAH. YOU KNOW?
I WANT TO GET TO KNOW HIM.

32:11.044 --> 32:12.445
YOU DO?

32:12.445 --> 32:13.680
YEAH.

32:13.680 --> 32:15.181
I MEAN, YOU TOLD ME ABOUT HIM
BEING MY DADDY,

32:15.181 --> 32:17.818
SO THE LEAST YOU COULD DO
IS LET ME GET TO KNOW HIM.

32:17.818 --> 32:20.687
YEAH. OKAY.

32:20.687 --> 32:22.756
OKAY.

32:24.424 --> 32:26.827
YEAH, I'M NOT ‐‐
I WON'T STAND IN YOUR WAY.

32:26.827 --> 32:28.862
OH, GOOD.
YOU GOT HIS NUMBER?

32:28.862 --> 32:29.996
NO.

32:33.600 --> 32:34.735
MAMA.

32:34.735 --> 32:37.704
I DON'T.

32:37.704 --> 32:40.473
WELL, CAN YOU GET IT?

32:40.473 --> 32:42.743
I ‐‐

32:42.743 --> 32:44.811
I'LL WORK ON IT.

32:56.356 --> 32:57.390
GOOD.

32:57.390 --> 33:00.200
GOOD.

33:01.434 --> 33:02.402
THANKS.

33:02.402 --> 33:03.737
WHATEVER.

33:03.737 --> 33:04.838
BOY, I LOVE YOU.

33:36.136 --> 33:37.804
YOU LOOKING FOR ME?

33:43.076 --> 33:44.110
YEAH.

33:46.379 --> 33:48.314
OKAY.

33:48.314 --> 33:51.151
CAN YOU PLEASE TELL THE MALONES
TO LEAVE ME ALONE?

33:51.151 --> 33:54.320
[ LIGHTER STRIKING ]

33:54.320 --> 33:57.490
THEY CAN BE ANIMALS,
CAN'T THEY?

33:57.490 --> 34:00.060
GIVE ME THAT.

34:00.060 --> 34:01.635
COME ON.

34:06.707 --> 34:07.741
YES.

34:11.244 --> 34:12.478
I CAN CALL THEM OFF.

34:12.478 --> 34:15.115
WHAT DO I NEED TO DO?

34:15.115 --> 34:16.482
TURN YOURSELF IN.

34:16.482 --> 34:18.151
WHY IS THAT
SO IMPORTANT TO YOU?

34:18.151 --> 34:19.553
HERE'S WHAT
YOU'RE GONNA DO.

34:19.553 --> 34:21.054
YOU'RE GONNA
TURN YOURSELF IN.

34:21.054 --> 34:22.556
YOU'RE GONNA
GO THROUGH TRIAL.

34:22.556 --> 34:25.125
AFTER ABOUT EIGHT MONTHS WHEN
THE WHOLE THING DIES DOWN,

34:25.125 --> 34:27.728
YOU'RE GOING TO BE MOVED
TO A MINIMUM‐SECURITY FACILITY,

34:27.728 --> 34:30.463
WHERE YOU WILL ESCAPE TO A CAR
THAT WILL TAKE YOU TO A PLANE

34:30.463 --> 34:33.767
THAT WILL TAKE TO MEXICO
WHERE YOU WILL STAY

34:33.767 --> 34:36.670
AND NEVER BE SEEN
OR HEARD FROM AGAIN.

34:36.670 --> 34:39.039
ALL I HAVE TO DO IS COP
TO THE WARRANTS I HAVE.

34:39.039 --> 34:41.474
AND ONE MORE.

34:41.474 --> 34:43.610
AND WHAT IS THAT?

34:45.512 --> 34:46.680
WHY DON'T YOU AND I
GO FOR A RIDE?

34:46.680 --> 34:47.781
I'LL FILL YOU IN.

34:47.781 --> 34:50.984
I DON'T DO
SEXUAL FAVORS.

34:53.987 --> 34:56.757
I'M NOT LOOKING
FOR SEXUAL FAVORS.

34:56.757 --> 34:59.826
I'M LOOKING FOR SOMEONE
WHO WILL LISTEN TO ME

34:59.826 --> 35:01.467
AND DO EXACTLY AS I SAY.

35:01.467 --> 35:03.069
DID YOU UNDERSTAND
"TURN YOURSELF IN"?

35:03.069 --> 35:04.337
DID YOU UNDERSTAND
"PRISON"?

35:04.337 --> 35:06.072
DID YOU UNDERSTAND
"ESCAPING" AND "MEXICO"

35:06.072 --> 35:07.508
AND ALL THAT STUFF,
THE AIRPLANE?

35:07.508 --> 35:09.576
YOU GOT ME?
YOU HEAR ME?

35:09.576 --> 35:10.677
THEN YOU GET IN THE CAR,

35:10.677 --> 35:14.314
YOU LISTEN TO ME
AND DO WHAT I SAY.

35:14.314 --> 35:16.517
OKAY.

35:16.517 --> 35:19.019
PUT THAT OUT.

35:28.729 --> 35:30.396
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

35:42.843 --> 35:43.844
HI.

35:43.844 --> 35:45.846
HI.

35:45.846 --> 35:46.847
JEFFERY?

35:46.847 --> 35:48.549
YEAH.

35:49.683 --> 35:51.852
WOW. YOUR MOM
SAID YOU WERE CUTE.

35:51.852 --> 35:53.486
[ CHUCKLES ]

35:53.486 --> 35:56.489
I'M MELISSA.
YEAH. HI.

35:56.489 --> 35:58.424
YOUR MOM WAS SO PERSISTENT
THAT WE MEET.

35:58.424 --> 36:00.360
MM, WELL, SHE ‐‐
SHE CAN BE THAT WAY.

36:00.360 --> 36:01.835
SHE TOLD ME
ALL ABOUT YOU.

36:01.835 --> 36:03.537
I'M SURE
SHE TOLD YOU ABOUT ME.

36:03.537 --> 36:05.872
KIND OF.

36:05.872 --> 36:08.208
I FELT LIKE
I WAS APPLYING FOR A JOB.

36:08.208 --> 36:10.176
[ CHUCKLES ] YEAH.
I KNOW THAT FEELING.

36:10.176 --> 36:12.513
THIS IS A NICE PLACE.

36:12.513 --> 36:15.281
EH.

36:15.281 --> 36:16.883
IT'S MY MOM'S FAVORITE.

36:16.883 --> 36:18.619
I CAN SEE WHY.
I LOVE HER STORY.

36:18.619 --> 36:21.221
SHE'S A BRILLIANT LAWYER.
I STUDIED ALL OF HER CASES.

36:21.221 --> 36:22.656
REALLY?

36:22.656 --> 36:25.058
YEAH. I'M GOING TO LAW SCHOOL
IN THE FALL.

36:25.058 --> 36:27.961
OH.
THAT'S ‐‐ THAT'S GREAT.

36:27.961 --> 36:30.163
HELLO.
WELCOME TO JUBILEE BLUE.

36:30.163 --> 36:32.032
CAN I TELL YOU
ABOUT MY SPECIALS?

36:32.032 --> 36:35.468
I JUST ‐‐ CAN I PLEASE
HAVE SOMETHING TO DRINK?

36:35.468 --> 36:37.003
SURE.
WHAT WOULD YOU LIKE?

36:37.003 --> 36:40.173
VODKA.
STRAIGHT.

36:40.173 --> 36:42.008
AND FOR THE LADY?

36:42.008 --> 36:43.009
I'D BETTER NOT.

36:43.009 --> 36:44.377
I'M A WILD WOMAN
WHEN I DRINK.

36:44.377 --> 36:46.079
OKAY.
SO, I GUESS ‐‐

36:46.079 --> 36:48.549
GIVE ME A DOUBLE BOURBON.

36:53.053 --> 36:55.722
WOW.
THAT'S ‐‐ THAT'S HARD.

36:55.722 --> 36:58.391
WHAT CAN I SAY?
I WAS IN A SORORITY ONCE.

36:58.391 --> 36:59.693
OH, YEAH.

36:59.693 --> 37:02.268
DON'T BLAME ME
IF I GET OUT OF CONTROL.

37:02.268 --> 37:04.504
OKAY.
I‐I‐I WON'T.

37:04.504 --> 37:07.040
AND DON'T TELL YOUR MOM
'CAUSE SHE THINKS I'M A SAINT.

37:07.040 --> 37:08.575
OH, GREAT.
D‐DOES SHE?

37:08.575 --> 37:09.743
YEAH,
BECAUSE SHE KNOWS MY MOM

37:09.743 --> 37:11.410
AND I WAS QUEEN OF THE
COTILLION. BLAH, BLAH, BLAH.

37:11.410 --> 37:12.411
MM‐HMM.

37:12.411 --> 37:14.180
I LIKE TO HAVE FUN.
DO YOU?

37:15.649 --> 37:17.116
OH, YEAH.
I DO.

37:17.116 --> 37:18.585
GOOD. BECAUSE THAT'S ALL
I REALLY WANT.

37:18.585 --> 37:19.986
I WANT TO WORK HARD
AND LIVE THE DREAM

37:19.986 --> 37:21.855
THAT I WANT FOR MYSELF
AND NOT WHAT MY PARENTS WANT.

37:21.855 --> 37:23.223
I MEAN, DO YOU ‐‐
DO YOU UNDERSTAND THAT?

37:23.223 --> 37:25.225
IT'S CRAZY HOW WE DO ALL THESE
THINGS IN LIFE AND JUST ‐‐

37:25.225 --> 37:26.727
OH, HEY, HEY, HEY.

37:26.727 --> 37:30.897
HEY, UH, C‐CAN YOU MAKE MINE
A DOUBLE, PLEASE?

37:30.897 --> 37:32.966
DO ALL THESE THINGS THAT
OUR PARENTS WANT US TO DO

37:32.966 --> 37:34.234
AND YOU JUST ‐‐ YEAH.
LIKE MY HAIR.

37:34.234 --> 37:35.769
LIKE, I WANT
TO WEAR MY HAIR CURLY,

37:35.769 --> 37:36.903
BUT SHE WANTS ME
TO WEAR MY HAIR STRAIGHT.

37:36.903 --> 37:38.639
IT'S RIDICULOUS.
I JUST CAN'T STAND IT.

37:38.639 --> 37:40.306
AND THEN, LIKE,
I HAVE THIS DOG, FIFI,

37:40.306 --> 37:41.441
AND SHE'S SO CUTE
AND I LOVE HER SO MUCH.

37:41.441 --> 37:42.609
[ GASPS ]

37:42.609 --> 37:44.110
MY MOM'S REALLY ANNOYING
ABOUT STUFF LIKE THAT.

37:44.110 --> 37:45.912
SHE MADE ME GO
TO THE COLLEGE.

37:45.912 --> 37:48.081
I LOVE TO GO SKIING.
IT'S SO MUCH FUN.

37:48.081 --> 37:50.216
I FELL ON MY BUTT
LIKE A MILLION TIMES.

37:50.216 --> 37:52.285
BUT I HAD THESE REALLY CUTE
PANTS, SO IT DIDN'T EVEN MATTER.

37:52.285 --> 37:53.820
MAYBE IF I JUST ‐‐
AS LONG AS YOU LOOK CUTE...

37:53.820 --> 37:55.589
HEY, CAN I HAVE ANOTHER,
PLEASE?

37:55.589 --> 37:57.724
...ON THE SLOPES,
DOES IT REALLY MATTER?

37:57.724 --> 37:58.925
OH, AND THIS TIME ‐‐
I DON'T KNOW.

37:58.925 --> 38:00.060
WHEN I WAS YOUNGER,
I WAS REALLY, REALLY FAT,

38:00.060 --> 38:01.101
AND MY MOM MADE ME GO
TO FAT CAMP.

38:01.101 --> 38:02.168
BUT IT WAS SO MUCH FUN

38:02.168 --> 38:03.469
BECAUSE I LEARNED HOW
TO PLAY THE CLARINET.

38:03.469 --> 38:05.038
I MEAN, DO YOU KNOW HOW
TO PLAY ANY INSTRUMENTS?

38:05.038 --> 38:06.573
I PLAY PIANO.
I PLAY CLARINET.

38:06.573 --> 38:08.174
I DO A COUPLE
DIFFERENT THINGS.

38:08.174 --> 38:10.376
AND SO, WHERE WOULD YOU
LIKE TO VACATION?

38:10.376 --> 38:11.512
FIJI'S SO MUCH FUN.

38:11.512 --> 38:13.780
DO YOU WANT KIDS?
HOW MANY KIDS DO YOU WANT?

38:13.780 --> 38:16.249
I WANT TO NAME MY CHILDREN
NATHANIEL, CRYSTAL,

38:16.249 --> 38:17.951
AND MAYBE FIONA.
I'M NOT REALLY SURE.

38:17.951 --> 38:19.686
I MEAN, THAT SOUNDS
LIKE A DOG'S NAME.

38:19.686 --> 38:21.254
I'M NOT REALLY SURE.
I DON'T KNOW.

38:21.254 --> 38:23.323
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

38:23.323 --> 38:26.893
CANDACE, PLEASE BE YOU AND
TELL ME YOU FORGOT YOUR KEY.

38:26.893 --> 38:28.161
DAD.

38:28.161 --> 38:29.462
GET YOUR THINGS.
I'M TAKING YOU HOME.

38:29.462 --> 38:30.463
COME ON.
WHAT?

38:30.463 --> 38:31.832
I'M TAKING YOU HOME
RIGHT NOW.

38:31.832 --> 38:32.833
GET YOUR THINGS.

38:32.833 --> 38:34.167
[ SIGHS ]
I AM HOME.

38:34.167 --> 38:37.270
AMANDA, I'M TAKING YOU
TO YOUR REAL HOME.

38:37.270 --> 38:38.438
GET YOUR THINGS NOW.

38:38.438 --> 38:40.206
NO, I'M NOT GOING.
LISTEN.

38:40.206 --> 38:41.441
I LOVE YOU VERY MUCH,

38:41.441 --> 38:43.443
BUT IF I HAVE TO CARRY YOU
OUT OF HERE PHYSICALLY,

38:43.443 --> 38:44.811
I PROMISE YOU
I WILL DO IT.

38:44.811 --> 38:46.613
IT'S BEEN A LONG WEEK.
I'M VERY TIRED.

38:46.613 --> 38:48.448
GET YOUR THINGS.
YOU'RE GOING HOME NOW.

38:48.448 --> 38:49.950
WHY CAN'T YOU
JUST LEAVE ME ALONE?!

38:49.950 --> 38:51.618
BECAUSE I LOVE YOU
TOO MUCH, SWEETHEART.

38:51.618 --> 38:53.486
I'M TAKING YOU HOME.

38:53.486 --> 38:54.955
WHAT ABOUT CANDACE?

38:54.955 --> 38:57.057
LEAVE CANDACE A NOTE.

38:57.057 --> 38:58.458
I'M NOT GOING BACK.

38:58.458 --> 39:00.834
YOU DON'T HAVE A CHOICE,
AMANDA.

39:00.834 --> 39:02.569
COME ON.
DAD, I ‐‐

39:02.569 --> 39:03.670
WHERE'S THE GUN?

39:05.672 --> 39:08.474
WHAT GUN?

39:08.474 --> 39:11.612
JEFFERY TOLD YOUR MOTHER
THAT YOU HAD BOUGHT A GUN.

39:11.612 --> 39:12.979
WHERE IS IT?

39:12.979 --> 39:16.416
IT'S A TOY.
HE'S SO NAIVE.

39:16.416 --> 39:17.651
A TOY?

39:17.651 --> 39:19.152
YEAH.

39:19.152 --> 39:20.554
WHERE IS IT?

39:20.554 --> 39:22.523
I DON'T KNOW.

39:22.523 --> 39:25.191
IT'S SOMEWHERE AROUND HERE.

39:28.361 --> 39:29.362
ALL RIGHT. COME ON.

39:29.362 --> 39:30.864
COME ON.
I NEED MY THINGS.

39:30.864 --> 39:32.899
I'LL GET SOMEBODY
TO PACK YOUR THINGS.

39:32.899 --> 39:35.335
I'M GONNA TAKE YOU HOME AND
I'M GONNA GET YOU SOME HELP.

39:35.335 --> 39:37.571
WHAT KIND OF HELP?

39:37.571 --> 39:40.040
SOMEONE TO TALK TO.
THAT'S ALL. COME ON.

39:40.040 --> 39:41.742
SO YOU THINK
I'M CRAZY AGAIN?

39:41.742 --> 39:43.544
NO, NO.
I DON'T THINK YOU'RE CRAZY.

39:43.544 --> 39:45.846
I THINK YOU NEED SOMEONE
TO TALK TO. THAT'S ALL.

39:45.846 --> 39:48.582
YOU PROMISE
I'M GOING HOME?

39:48.582 --> 39:51.918
I PROMISE.

39:51.918 --> 39:54.354
YOU'RE NOT GONNA
LOCK ME AWAY?

39:54.354 --> 39:56.657
NO, NO.

39:56.657 --> 39:58.491
I PROMISED YOU
I'D NEVER DO THAT AGAIN

39:58.491 --> 40:00.326
AND I WON'T DO THAT AGAIN.

40:00.326 --> 40:02.235
WE'RE GOING HOME.
OKAY?

40:02.235 --> 40:03.504
OKAY.

40:03.504 --> 40:04.505
ALL RIGHT.
COME ON.

40:04.505 --> 40:06.940
I'LL GO.
GOOD.

40:06.940 --> 40:08.408
UM, I NEED MY PURSE.

40:10.076 --> 40:11.344
OKAY.

40:14.080 --> 40:16.482
I'M READY.
ALL RIGHT.

40:36.236 --> 40:38.171
[ MUFFLED CRYING ]

40:39.540 --> 40:42.342
MAKE THIS EASY
ON YOURSELF, HONEY.

40:42.342 --> 40:45.378
DON'T RESIST.
[ Crying ] PLEASE!

40:45.378 --> 40:48.314
PLEASE!

40:48.314 --> 40:49.816
ON YOUR KNEES, HONEY.

40:49.816 --> 40:52.018
NO, WAIT.
NO, I PROMISE YOU ‐‐

40:52.018 --> 40:53.453
THEN YOU'LL BE SHOT
IN THE FACE.

40:53.453 --> 40:55.756
I WON'T BOTHER HIM.
COME ON.

40:55.756 --> 40:57.457
DON'T MAKE THIS UGLIER.
COME ON!

40:57.457 --> 41:00.226
NO! NO. NO!

41:00.226 --> 41:01.234
GET ON YOUR KNEES.

41:01.234 --> 41:02.503
[ CRYING ]

41:12.412 --> 41:14.047
DO IT!
NO!

41:14.047 --> 41:15.215
[ GUNSHOT ]

41:15.215 --> 41:17.083
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

41:17.083 --> 41:18.118
LET'S GO.

41:23.056 --> 41:24.591
GO, GO, GO, GO.

41:31.264 --> 41:33.399
<i>NEXT ON "THE HAVES</i>
<i>AND THE HAVE NOTS"...</i>

41:33.399 --> 41:35.435
THE CAB DRIVER'S
GONNA BRING YOU HOME.

41:35.435 --> 41:37.571
I'M GOING TO YOUR PLACE.
I'M NOT THAT KIND OF GUY.

41:38.404 --> 41:39.906
Man: YO.

41:39.906 --> 41:41.508
I'M LOOKING FOR CANDY.

41:41.508 --> 41:43.476
AIN'T NOBODY SEEN HER
IN A FEW DAYS.

41:43.476 --> 41:44.745
AMANDA, HOW ARE YOU?

41:44.745 --> 41:46.246
I DON'T WANT TO BE HERE.

41:46.246 --> 41:47.413
DID YOU FIND THE GUN?

41:47.413 --> 41:48.649
WHAT ARE YOU DOING,
BABY?

41:48.649 --> 41:50.016
WHAT ARE YOU WANDERING
AROUND THE HOUSE FOR?

41:50.016 --> 41:51.618
WE JUST NEED
YOUR COOPERATION

41:51.618 --> 41:53.587
TO BRING CHARGES
AGAINST WYATT CRYER.

41:53.587 --> 41:55.756
JEFFERY, DO YOU THINK
THIS MAKES YOU STRAIGHT NOW?

41:55.756 --> 41:57.157
IS EVERYTHING OKAY?

41:59.359 --> 42:00.934
HOLD ON A SECOND.
